                                trustees to determine benefit allocation
                            </li>
                            <li class="bigtfont" ; align="left" style="color:#000000">Tax calculation is applied</li>
                            <li class="bigtfont" ; align="left" style="color:#000000">Bank verification is received</li>
                            <li class="bigtfont" ; align="left" style="color:#000000">Payment is made</li>

                        </p>

